
# Releasing

This file summarizes how to prepare a new cdg release.

$Id: RELEASING,v 1.1 2005-12-16 21:48:00 blair Exp $

---

* Test
  % ant clean && ant grouper && ant grouper-cvs-db-init
  % ant test
  % ./test-cli.sh
* Tag and tarball
  % cvs tag CDG_MAJOR_MINOR[_PATCH]
  % cvs export -r$TAG -d ./cdg-$VERSION com.devclue.grouper
  % changelog > ./cdg-$VERSION/doc/CHANGES
  % ant javadoc
  % mv doc/html ./cdg-$VERSION/doc/html
  % tar czvf ./cdg-$VERSION.tgz ./cdg-$VERSION

